{"tid":1823484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"華記寫信俾朱克伯格 對被封鎖帳戶不滿","createTime":"2020-01-13T17:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T20:11:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":70,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"a81af9e8b569aa2abc40950c3fdd09ebda2601e8","tid":1823484,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yt3.ggpht.com/C5H_vd9CkVKnjdO5hRDci43hixkGHvjYCeF-inqlejODOVQMaEzfwQySnyN8Zes5K1uHPkCl4HyXVQ=s1024-nd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyt3.ggpht.com%2FC5H_vd9CkVKnjdO5hRDci43hixkGHvjYCeF-inqlejODOVQMaEzfwQySnyN8Zes5K1uHPkCl4HyXVQ%3Ds1024-nd&h=0871ac0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你好！馬克（Facebook創始人）<br />\n祝您2020年快樂，並祝您和您的家人幸福。<br />\n我叫Alex Yeung，我是一家在亞洲開展業務的小小商人。<br />\n請允許我與Facebook分享我最近的經驗，因為我了解您在聆聽並重視用戶體驗的反饋。<br />\n我最初在2019年建立了我的Facebook帳戶，名為Alex Yeung Channel華記正能量。它已於2019年11月22日被取消。我立即以New Alex Yeung頻道華記正能量的名義重新設置了該帳戶，並於2020年1月4日被取消。我剛剛於2020年1月9日重新建立了該帳戶，不確定Facebook何時會再次取消<br />\n另請注意，所有取消操作都是在最近幾個月進行的，這非常令人討厭<br />\n所有取消均不作任何通知，解釋或補救措施。這種突然的取消令人不安。我不僅立即失去了與粉絲的交流，還失去了在全球發布的內容。<br />\n總而言之，作為這個社交媒體的撰稿人，這對我來說是不公平的。<br />\n我堅信法律和命令，請告知其內容是否一直在遵守Facebook用戶的條款和條件。這種待遇在Facebook上散佈，不受信任和令人沮喪<br />\n<br />\n期待您的回音<br />\n<br />\n真誠的Alex上<br />\n來自：中國香港<br />\n電子郵件：yeungkwun108@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHi my name is alex from Hong Kong<br />\nI just write a letter to Facebook founder <br />\nMr Mark Zuckerberg<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHello Mark, （Facebook Founder)<br />\nHappy 2020 and  best wishes  for you and your family. <br />\nMy name is Alex Yeung , I am an entrepreneur with businesses across Asia.  <br />\nAllow me to share my recent experience with facebook as I understand you listen and value feedback of user experience. <br />\nI initially setup my Facebook account in 2019 call Alex Yeung Channel 華記正能量. It was cancelled on 22nd Nov 2019. I  immediately re-setup the account under the name of New Alex Yeung channel 華記正能量and it was cancelled on 4th Jan 2020. I have just re-established the account on 9th Jan 2020 and is unsure when Facebook will cancel it again   <br />\nPlease also note that all this cancellation occurred with the last few months and is extremely annoying <br />\nAll cancellations are with no notification, explanation or remediation actions  .This abrupt cancellation is disturbing . Not only I lost communication with my fans immediately I also lost the content that I&rsquo;ve posted globally. <br />\nAll in all, it is unfair to me as a contributor to this social media.  <br />\nI am a strong believer of laws and orders and please advise if the content has been observing the terms and conditions of Facebook users. This treatment is distributing, untrusted and discouraging on Facebook <br />\n<br />\nLooking forward to hearing from you<br />\n<br />\nSincerely<br />\nAlex Yeung <br />\nFrom:Hong Kong CHINA<br />\nEmail: yeungkwun108 @gmail.com"},{"pid":"917694728d6505a43c3f992fc3fb6d6812db2db7","tid":1823484,"uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk